=Description=

"The openCoLab is a network of people and organisations working together to create a new economy which supports sustainable and vibrant communities. It is our belief and experience that:

* “things happen when you connect people together” 

* “great things happen when you connect great people together.”

We work with organisations, communities and individuals to create new social and economic systems, business models and services using blockchain technology and associated decentralised applications.  Our mandate and manifesto is to show and share – to not only imagine; but bring to life a better future.

We do things that matter – because it matters."


